But Tang Wu­tong ac­tu­ally needs to stim­u­late to move­ment own Soul Power to re­sist the chill in the air, but she is Ti­tled Douluo rank Soul Mas­ter, Dragon-But­ter­fly Douluo is not Bai Jiao, this cold could not have threat­ened her. 但唐舞桐却需要催动自身魂力来抵抗寒意了,不过她是封号斗罗级别魂师,龙蝶斗罗可不是白叫的,这点寒冷还威胁不到她。 „Wu­tong, we, if re­sists in this icy seas, you are not my match.” Huo Yuhao said with a smile. “舞桐,我们要是在这冰海上对抗,你可不是我的对手哦。”霍雨浩笑着说道。 [Say / Way] that Tang Wu­tong some are not con­vinced: „Hasn't tried to know? It is not con­vinced we to hit one time again.” 唐舞桐有些不服气的道:“没试过怎么知道？不服气我们再打一次。” „Does not want. I have not fought you, has won you, I love dearly. Lost, my anx­i­ety. This makes me in­nate lack fights **, how to fight you?” Huo Yuhao said with a smile. “不要。我可不跟你打了,赢了你,我心疼。输了,我肉疼。这让我先天就缺乏战斗**,怎么跟你打？”霍雨浩笑着说道。 Tang Wu­tong beats his lightly, on the face also full is the happy ex­pres­sion. 唐舞桐轻捶他一下,脸上也已经满是笑意。 They fly to the icy seas, the speed of flight is not fast. In the sur­face seems like re­laxed, but the Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power time is ac­tu­ally scan­ning the sound of sur­round­ing icy seas. Even the thor­ough sea water car­ries on to search to ob­serve. 两人向冰海内部飞行,飞行的速度却并不快。表面上看似轻松,但霍雨浩的精神力却时刻都在扫描着周围冰海的动静。甚至深入海水进行探察。 Under the ice sur­face, many ma­rine life are pa­trolling , many sea Soul Beast exist. How­ever, so long as they feel the for­mi­da­ble aura that on Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong lend, does not dare hur­riedly to at­tack them. 冰面下,有不少海洋生物在游弋,其中也不乏一些海魂兽存在。不过,它们只要感受到霍雨浩和唐舞桐身上散发出的强大气息,就不敢造次来攻击他们了。 ex­ceed flies to north, the tem­per­a­ture be­comes lower. The float­ing ice quan­tity in icy seas also be­came more and more. Giant ice­bergs find at every­where. Some are spe­cially huge, looks like piece of small land. 越向北飞行,气温就变得越低。冰海上的浮冰数量也变得越来越多了。一座座巨大的冰山随处可见。一些特别巨大的,就像是一片小型陆地似的。 On ice sur­face, ex­is­tences of some sea Soul Beast, eying cov­etously vis­its them, ac­tu­ally does not ap­proach. The Soul Beast sen­sa­tion is very keen, Huo Yuhao and Tang W