f Huo Yuhao. “好！”霍雨浩点头答应,雪帝有些恋恋不舍的看了一眼周围的冰海,这才重新回到霍雨浩体内去了。她不是不想和霍雨浩一起在这冰海上方飞行,而是因为这种高速飞行过程中,她如果在外面,会加大霍雨浩的消耗。 After yes­ter­day's and a Tang Wu­tong war, the Huo Yuhao pre­sent self-con­fi­dence was stronger. He and Tang Wu­tong col­lab­o­rates, even if gen­eral Tran­scen­dent Douluo is not their matches. Even if the match is more for­mi­da­ble, can­not hit, couldn't have been in­escapable? Let alone above this icy seas, his strength has enor­mous am­pli­fi­ca­tion, did not say other, these solid ice all are his Ice Ex­plo­sion Tech­nique con­duc­tor. Even if fac­ing mas­sive sea Soul Beast, does not need to fear any­thing. 经过昨天和唐舞桐一战,霍雨浩现在的自信心更强了。他和唐舞桐联手,就算是一般的超级斗罗都不是他们对手。哪怕是对手更加强大一些,打不过,难道还跑不了么？更何况在这冰海之上,他的实力有极大的增幅,不说别的,那些坚冰就全都是他那冰爆术的导体。哪怕是面对大量海魂兽,也不需要惧怕什么。 The hand of Tang Wu­tong, they are main­tain­ing at the icy seas sea level kilo­me­ter about ac­cel­er­ates to fly highly, thor­ough icy seas. Al­though Huo Yuhao is self-con­fi­dent, but ab­solutely does not have the gen­eral idea, he is al­ways re­leas­ing Spir­i­tual De­tec­tion, is feel­ing nearby all changes. 拉着唐舞桐的手,两人保持在冰海海面千米左右的高度加速飞行,深入冰海。霍雨浩虽然自信,但却绝对没有大意,他始终释放着精神探测,感受着附近的一切变化。 Sky over the icy seas lit­tle has Soul Beast to ap­pear, at least they fly, had not dis­cov­ered that any Soul Beast ex­ists. Ob­vi­ously, here re­gard­ing flight Soul Beast, is just like for­bid­den area gen­eral ex­is­tence. 冰海上空很少有魂兽出现,至少他们一路飞来,就没有发现任何魂兽存在。显然,这里对于飞行魂兽来说,乃是宛如禁区一般的存在。 In an in­stant, half dou­ble-hour passed by, they could not feel any land com­pletely the aura. How­ever, in the sea level the vol­ume huge ice­berg is also more and more, looks to­ward the dis­tant place, even is snow-white one piece, the sea level was very dif­fi­cult to see. But here tem­per­a­ture, al­ready also the tem­per­a­ture of more and more close Ex­treme North Tun­dra cen­tral area. 转眼间,半个时辰过去了,他们已经完全感受不到任何陆地的气息。不过,海面上体积庞大的冰山也是越来越多,朝更远处望去,甚至是白皑皑的一片,海面都很难看到了。而这里的温度,已经也越来越接近极北冰原核心圈的温度。 Huo Yuhao is shak­ing the hand of Tang Wu­tong, in­h