, the ice-cold vi­sion are look­ing in their di­rec­tions. 远处一座巨大的冰山上,一道道冰冷的目光正朝着他们的方向看过来。 That is an only giant ma­rine life, takes a broad view to look, sev­eral hun­dreds, all crawl fully on an ice­berg. Be­cause Huo Yuhao feels their in­tense hos­til­i­ties, this has held on Tang Wu­tong. 那是一只只巨大的海洋生物,放眼望去,足有数百之多,全都匍匐在一座冰山上。霍雨浩正是因为感受到它们强烈的敌意,这才拉住了唐舞桐。 „What is that?” Tang Wu­tong some­what cu­ri­ous looks to dis­tant place. “那是什么？”唐舞桐有些好奇的看向远处。 Her vi­sion is in­fe­rior to Huo Yuhao, but with the Spir­i­tual De­tec­tion help of Huo Yuhao, sit­u­a­tion that can also feel some dis­tant places. 她的视力不如霍雨浩,但在霍雨浩的精神探测帮助下,也能感受到一些远处的情况。 That is one only seems all over the body swarthy Soul Beast, the build size varies, the biggest body has about sev­eral me­ters con­sid­er­able, the whole body is send­ing out the pale blue halo. Small­est, be only more than one meter are long. On each mouth grows two sharp long buck­teeth. 那是一只只看上去通体黝黑的魂兽,体型大小不一,最大的身长足有十几米开外,全身都散发着淡蓝色的光晕。个头最小的只有一米多长。每一只嘴上都长出两根尖长的獠牙。 „Sea Devil Ele­phant! These many.” Huo Yuhao knit the brows. “海魔象！这么多。”霍雨浩皱了皱眉。 Sea Devil Ele­phant is one in sea Soul Beast, and has the rep­re­sen­ta­tion very much. Al­though human Soul Mas­ter are not many to the sea Soul Beast un­der­stand­ing, but ini­tially when the Shrek Acad­emy study, had the in­tro­duc­tion to this Soul Beast. 海魔象是海魂兽中的一种,而且很有代表性。人类魂师虽然对海魂兽了解不多,但当初在史莱克学院学习的时候,对这种魂兽还是有介绍的。 Sea Devil Ele­phant is dis­po­si­tion rel­a­tively docile Soul Beast, they most major char­ac­ter­is­tics have the strong de­fen­sive power. Sea Devil Ele­phant that grow­ing up, height over over seven me­ters, so-called grown, over hun­dred years cul­ti­vate are. Seven me­ters huge body is quite ma­jes­tic, only thick­ness over ten cen­time­ters of skin. Their skins are quite tena­cious, has the strong re­sis­tance to any phys­i­cal at­tack. But Sea Devil Ele­phant in this icy seas, per­haps will be also strong re­gard­ing Ice At­tribute and fire at­tribute at­tack re­sis­tance. 海魔象是一种性格相对温顺的魂兽,它们最大的特点就是有着超强的防御力。一只成年的海魔象,身长会超过七米以上,所谓成年,就是有百年以上修为。七米长的庞大身躯极为雄壮,单是皮肤的厚度就会超过十厘米。它们的皮肤极为坚韧,对任何物理攻击都有超强抗性。而这冰海之中的海魔象,恐怕对于冰属性和火属性的攻击抗性也会非常强。 Nat­u­rally, any Soul Beast has good and bad points. Com­pares in its for­mi­da­ble de­fen­sive power, the strik­ing power and speed were its short board. 当然,任何魂兽都有优缺点。相比于它强大的防御力,攻击力和速度就是它的短板了。 Sea Devil Ele­phant only then in the water, speed will pro­mote, but be­side water sur­face, speed ac­tu­ally slow. As for their at­tacks, only then some con­trol water or the ice abil­ity, is not too strong. 海魔象只有在水中,速度才会提升起来,但在水面之外,速度却慢的很。至于它们的攻击,只有一些操控水或者冰的能力,都不算太强。 Sea Devil Ele­phant is one type lives in groups Soul Beast, gen­er­ally speak­ing, is sev­eral is a tribal group. One has sev­eral hun­dred sit­u­a­tions like, at least has not men­tioned in the Shrek Acad­emy teach­ing. 海魔象是一种群居魂兽,一般来说,都是十几只为一个族群。像这样一下就出现数百只的情况,至少在史莱克学院的教学中是没有提到过的。 Huo Yuhao looked at one, has made the ac­cu­rate judg­ment, „cul­ti­vat­ing of these Sea Devil Ele­phant for gen­eral, strongest is also ten thou­sand years cul­ti­vates is, there are three. Sur­plus any­thing cul­ti­vate to have, ten years. Ev­i­dently, here should be their habi­tats.” 霍雨浩只是看了一眼,就做出了准确判断,“这些海魔象的修为都一般,最强的也不过就是万年修为,有三只。剩余的什么修为都有,还有十年的。看样子,这里应该是它们的栖息地。” On the side of Huo Yuhao was ex­plain­ing to Tang Wu­tong, drew her to start off. This rank cul­ti­vates for Sea Devil Ele­phant for them sol­dier not any threat. More­over they in kilo­me­ter al­ti­tude fly­ing, by un­der­stand­ing of Huo Yuhao Sea Devil Ele­phant, even if ten thou­sand years cul­ti­vates is, can­not at­tack the abil­ity kilo­me­ter away. 霍雨浩一边向唐舞桐解释着,也拉着她重新上路。这种级别修为的海魔象对他们来说兵没有任何威胁。而且他们在千米高空飞行,以霍雨浩对海魔象的了解,就算是万年修为的,也没有能够攻击千米外的能力。 Flies and that's the end, in his opin­ion, this is just this icy seas to the small in­ter­lude of trip. 飞过去就是了,在他看来,这只不过是此次冰海之旅的一个小插曲而已。 The speed that Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong from the sky fly is quick, must fly from the ice­berg of Sea Devil Ele­phant group life shortly. 霍雨浩和唐舞桐在空中飞行的速度很快,眼看着就要从海魔象群生活的冰山上飞过。 In this time, sud­denly, was sev­eral Sea Devil Ele­phant of head was tak­ing out a strange thing re­spec­tively, that was one only seems pre­sents for the pale golden big conch, al­to­gether 12 Sea Devil Ele­phant took out this conch, then made an ef­fort to move, sent out low and deep „hum” sound. 正在这时,突然间,为首的几只海魔象各自取出了一个奇异的东西,那是一只只看上去呈献为淡金色的大海螺,一共12只海魔象取出了这种海螺,然后用力吹动,发出低沉的“呜呜”声。 „Hum” sound re­sounds, Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong are the com­plex­ion change, be­cause they feel clearly that sur­round­ing air sud­denly one tight, all air cur­rents as if all van­ished. Their bod­ies crash im­me­di­ately rapidly down­ward. “呜呜”声才一响起,霍雨浩和唐舞桐都是脸色一变,因为他们清楚的感觉到,周围的空气猛然一紧,紧接着,所有气流仿佛全都消失了似的。他们的身体顿时急速向下坠落。 Must know that any liv­ing thing from the sky flies, in fact must de­pend on the air cur­rent. Through im­pact of Soul Power to air cur­rent, thus main­tains from the sky flies. 要知道,任何生物在空中飞行,实际上还是都要依托于气流的。通过魂力对气流的冲击,从而保持在空中飞行。 After all air cur­rents in air even are all ma­te­ri­als van­ish, they like ap­pear­ing in in­com­pa­ra­bly clean vac­uum. Nowhere with the strength, re­ceives the at­trac­tion of earth's at­trac­tion, falls in­stan­ta­neously to under. Even if were be­hind them nine lev­els of Flight Soul Guid­ance De­vice in this case does not play role. Wing that opens with the aid of air cur­rent, is the fu­tile ef­fort. 而当空气中的所有气流甚至是一切物质都消失之后,他们就像出现在无比干净的真空之中。无处借力之下,受到地心引力的吸引,瞬间就向下方落去。哪怕是他们背后的九级飞行魂导器在这种情况下都起不到作用了。张开的翅翼借助不到气流,也是徒劳的。 Crashes to under from the kilo­me­ter upper air, this did not joke. Al­though Huo Yuhao does not know that these Sea Devil Ele­phant have made any­thing, but faces the cri­sis, he can al­ways main­tain calm. 从千米高空向下方坠落,这可不是闹着玩的。霍雨浩虽然不知道那些海魔象做了些什么,但面对危机,他总能保持冷静。 Gets hold of Tang Wu­tong hand gen­tly. Tang Wu­tong ar­rived at him im­me­di­ately be­hind, both hands hold in the arms his waist, back dragon wings opens fully in a big way. 握紧唐舞桐的手轻轻一拉。唐舞桐立刻就到了他身后,双手搂住他的腰,背后龙翼全力张开到最大。 Al­though did not have air cur­rent to exist in the air, in the process that they are tenes­mus­ing rapidly many will pro­duce some air cur­rents. So long as can draw sup­port pre­vi­ous, the speed that they tenes­mus will re­duce. 尽管在空气中已经没有气流存在,他们在急速下坠的过程中多少还是会产生一些气流的。只要能借助上一点,他们下坠的速度就会降低。 ------------------------------------------------ ------------------------------------------------ In our pres­tige - plat­form, every­body trans­mits: Peer­less Tang Sect 121, the con­sult is lat­est the peer­less Tang Sect car­toon, as be­fore is five salvos! Five fine car­toons give to every­body. 在我们的威信-平台,大家发送:绝世唐门121,查阅最新绝世唐门漫画,依旧是五连发哦！五张精美漫画送给大家。 Joins our plat­forms to be very sim­ple, pres­tige - top right-hand cor­ner plus sign - in­creases friend - pub­lic ac­count num­ber - searches Tang three few, has the au­then­ti­ca­tion, is our fam­i­lies. 加入我们的平台很简单,威信-右上角加号-添加朋友-公众账号-搜索唐家三少,带认证的,就是我们的家哦。 The quick­est re­newal, non- ball win­dow read­ing in­vited. 最快更新,无弹窗阅读请。

