DD2 - V.#11 - #540 Under icy seas


Mean­while, in the Huo Yuhao eye golden light puts greatly, Tang Wu­tong can feel clearly through Spir­i­tual Shar­ing that Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power has locked di­rectly float­ing ice in their under sea level. 与此同时,霍雨浩眼中金光大放,唐舞桐通过精神共享能够清楚的感觉到,霍雨浩的精神力直接就锁定了他们正下方海面上的一块浮冰。 The Huo Yuhao left hand makes an ef­fort to grip tightly. Only lis­tens to „bang” a bang, that float­ing ice sud­denly scrap. The for­mi­da­ble ex­plo­sive force leads the air cur­rent and sea water shoots up to the sky. 紧接着,霍雨浩左手用力攥紧。只听“轰”的一声巨响,那块浮冰骤然炸碎。强大的爆炸力带动气流与海水冲天而起。 But at this time, Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong had about 300 me­ters in the process mid­dle dis­tance sea level that for­merly rapidly tenes­mused. 而此时,霍雨浩和唐舞桐已经在先前急速下坠的过程中距离海面只有300米左右了。 This air cur­rent to pre­vi­ous, the Tang Wu­tong wings takes ad­van­tage of some­body's au­thor­ity im­me­di­ately in air­borne one slow. Melted their for­merly brunt­ing. Then fell to­ward the sea level. 这股气流向上一顶,唐舞桐的双翼顿时借势在空中一缓。化解掉两人先前的冲势。然后才朝着海面上落了下去。 300 me­ters this al­ti­tude, re­gard­ing their this cul­ti­vated for the pow­er­house, is not any­thing. 300米这个高度,对于他们这等修为的强者来说,已经不算什么了。 The Tang Wu­tong wil­low eye­brows are but ac­tu­ally ver­ti­cal, two items of cir­cles open the eyes, are look­ing an­grily at the Sea Devil Ele­phant group of dis­tant place, the pow­er­ful im­pos­ing man­ner raised to gather in­stan­ta­neously. The right hand lifts, Golden Dragon Spear was al­ready grasp­ing. 唐舞桐柳眉倒竖,二目圆睁,怒视着远处的海魔象群,强盛的气势瞬间就提聚了起来。右手一抬,黄金龙枪已然在握。 Also no won­der she will be angry, their flights for­ward in good con­di­tion, have not gone to pro­voke these Sea Devil Ele­phant, these Sea Devil Ele­phant ac­tu­ally sud­denly launched the at­tack to them. More­over this at­tack is fatal, if has not dealt ap­pro­pri­ately, falls from that high place, below most places are the ice­bergs, al­most must die with­out doubt! 也难怪她会生气,两人好端端的向前飞行,跟本就没去招惹那些海魔象,这些海魔象却突然向他们发起了攻击。而且这攻击可是致命的,如果没有合适应对的话,从那么高的地方摔下来,下面大多数地方都是冰山,几乎是必死无疑啊！ That moves 12 Sea Devil Ele­