we come the icy seas to be harm­less, but wants to seek for a Sea Princess clan, your ex­cel­lency at­tacks rashly, did not fear that brings the dis­as­ter to own clans­man?” 霍雨浩皱眉道:“阁下。并不是所有的人类都该死,我们前来冰海并无恶意,只是想去寻找海公主一族,阁下贸然攻击,就不怕给自己的族人带来灾祸么？” That only huge Sea Devil Ele­phant angry roared, in the fore­leg was grasp­ing the golden conch made an ef­fort has wielded, ex­uded „hum” sound once more. 那只巨大的海魔象愤怒的咆哮一声,前肢中握着的金色海螺用力的挥动了一下,再次发出“呜呜”声。 „You. Must die! You also dare to look for Sea Princess. En­ters icy seas world, you must die!” Its words some­what speak in­co­her­ently, but let the Huo Yuhao clear feel­ing the ex­tremely in­tense hos­til­ity. “你们。都要死！你们还敢来找海公主。进入冰海世界,你们都要死！”它的话语有些语无伦次,但却让霍雨浩清楚的感受到了极其强烈的敌意。 Huo Yuhao this time comes is not and sea Soul Beast for the enemy, po­lar­ity. He hopes that can also es­tab­lish with sea Soul Beast is sim­i­lar to with Star Dou For­est such re­la­tions, if so, the place of human gain spirit dra­mat­i­cally will in­crease. Thus lets many Soul Mas­ter choice spirit, but does not kill Soul Beast to gain Soul Ring. 霍雨浩这次前来并不是与海魂兽为敌的,正相反。他希望能够和海魂兽也建立起如同和星斗大森林那样的关系,如果是那样的话,人类获取魂灵的地方就会大幅度增加。从而让更多的魂师选择魂灵,而并非杀死魂兽获取魂环。 There­fore, he sup­presses the spunk in heart, the sink­ing sound track: „Your ex­cel­lency, please does not want self to harm. We do not want to kill your clans­man.” 所以,他压住心中的怒意,沉声道:“阁下,请不要自误。我们不想杀害你的族人。” At this time, two sides Sea Devil Ele­phant have com­pleted sur­round­ing, and fast threw to­ward Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong di­rec­tion. On some Sea Devil Ele­phant the blue light twin­kle, emits ice balls to­ward Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong. 此时,两边的海魔象已经完成了包围,并且快速的朝着霍雨浩和唐舞桐的方向扑了过来。一些海魔象身上蓝光闪烁,朝着霍雨浩和唐舞桐喷吐出一颗颗冰弹。 These ice balls ice the blue color all over the body, from the sky has de­lim­ited, has the in­tense Soul Power fluc­tu­a­tion to ap­pear ob­vi­ously. 这些冰弹通体冰蓝色,在空中划过的时候,明显有强烈魂力波动出现。 This is the Ice Ex­plo­sion ball! One of Soul Abil­ity Sea Devil Ele­phant most ex­cels , is also their tal­ent Soul Abil­