that the Sea Devil Ele­phant leader trans­mits for all that but he has ac­tu­ally put down the golden conch in hand. “吼！海公主已经发下禁令,一切进入我们冰海范围内的人类,都是敌人,都要毁灭。就算你放过我们,也还会有其他海魂兽对付你们。”海魔象首领传递出的精神意念虽然如此,但他却已经放下了手中的金色海螺。 Huo Yuhao some­what cu­ri­ous looks to its golden conch, said: „What thing are you? Why will make us crash from the sky.” 霍雨浩有些好奇的看向它那金色海螺,道:“你这是什么东西？为什么会让我们从天空中坠落。” „Tri­ton, bans spa­tially!” The Sea Devil Ele­phant leader has not con­cealed. “法螺,禁空！”海魔象首领并没有隐瞒。 Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong look at each other one, they saw each other dig­nity in eye. 霍雨浩和唐舞桐对视一眼,两人都看出了彼此眼中的凝重。 Rea­son that they have enter in icy seas range self-con­fi­dently, a biggest rea­son is the fly­ing abil­ity. In sea Soul Beast, over­whelm­ing ma­jori­ties are un­able to fly, even if can fly, im­pos­si­ble to com­pete the speed with them. There­fore they mo­men­tar­ily can re­treat. But this Sea Devil Ele­phant clan is not in sea Soul Beast ob­vi­ously for­mi­da­ble, but had this to ban the spa­tial conch. Such looks like, sea Soul Beast had sim­i­lar method in­evitably. 他们之所以有自信进入冰海范围内,其中一个最大的原因就是飞行能力。海魂兽之中,绝大多数都无法飞行,就算能够飞行,也不可能与他们比拼速度。所以他们随时都可以退走。而这海魔象一族在海魂兽中明显算不上强大,但却就具备了这禁空的海螺。这么看来,海魂兽必然是掌握了很多类似手段。 They can­not from the sky fight, then, can ac­tu­ally let the flight or is Soul Beast falls in the air­borne per­son. No won­der sky over this Bound­less sea area could not see that flight Soul Beast ex­ists, per­haps al­ready in all per­ished with the sea Soul Beast bat­tle. 它们不能在空中战斗,那么,却可以让飞行在空中的人或者是魂兽落下来。难怪这浩瀚的海域上空都看不到飞行魂兽存在呢,恐怕早就在和海魂兽的争斗中全都灭亡了吧。 „Said good­bye.” Huo Yuhao knows that does not have what truth to say with these Sea Devil Ele­phant. How­ever the con­flict by no means com­pletely was also use­less, first they knew had in sea Soul Beast bans the spa­tial method. Next is a Sea Princess clan re­gard­ing hos­til­ity of hu­man­ity. “告辞了。”霍雨浩知道,和这些海魔象是没有什么道理可讲的。不过刚才的冲突也并非完全无用,首先他们就知道了在海魂兽之中是拥有一些禁空手段的。其次就是海公主一族对于人类的仇视。 Their sec­ond sor­tie, but, these time ac­tu­ally ob­vi­ously dropped the al­ti­tude. After all, once the match bans spa­tial method to use, in process of tenes­mus­ing they in­evitably are very pas­sive. More high of fly­ing, the pas­sive time is also longer. 两人再次起飞,不过,这一次却明显下降了高度。毕竟,一旦对手禁空手段使用出来,在下坠的过程中他们必然是十分被动的。飞的越高,被动的时间也就越长。 Main­tains at the dis­tance sea level about 500 me­ters al­ti­tude, this al­ti­tude, even if crashes di­rectly, will not re­ceive any­thing to in­jure. Nat­u­rally, is away from the sea level to be nearer, they the prob­lem that may en­counter will be also more. 保持在距离海面500米左右的高度,这种高度,就算是直接坠落下来,也不会受到什么伤害。当然,距离海面越近,他们有可能遇到的麻烦也就会更多。

