Huo Yuhao con­trolled back nine lev­els of Flight Soul Guid­ance De­vice to slow down the speed, said: „We are are not being far away from the icy seas prob­a­bly, but is con­tin­u­ing thor­ough as. Wa­ter­mark ad­ver­tise­ment test wa­ter­mark ad­ver­tise­ment test” 霍雨浩控制着背后的九级飞行魂导器放缓了速度,道:“我们好像并不是在远离冰海,而是在继续深入似的。水印广告测试水印广告测试” „Um?” [Say / Way] of Tang Wu­tong doubts: „Can­not! From the po­si­tion of Sun, we are to re­turn­ing to fly are right. How can not be right?” “嗯？”唐舞桐疑惑的道:“不会啊！从太阳的位置来看,我们就是在向回飞行才对。怎么会不对呢？” Huo Yuhao more is the think­ing more does not think right, he stopped sim­ply, closes eyes, is feel­ing the sur­round­ing all silently. After long time, his sud­den com­plex­ion big change, „is not right, our fall into trap.” 霍雨浩越是思索越是觉得不对,他索性停了下来,闭上双眼,默默地感受着周围的一切。半晌之后,他突然脸色大变,“不对,我们中计了。” Tang Wu­tong hear of his such say­ing, is in the heart one tight, in the eye golden light dodges, Golden Dragon Spear ap­pears in the hand. 唐舞桐听他这么一说,也是心中一紧,眼中金光一闪,黄金龙枪就出现在手中。 The Huo Yuhao com­plex­ion is very ugly, by his Spir­i­tual Power, flew to have about half dou­ble-hour the dis­cov­ery not to be right un­ex­pect­edly fully, it can be imag­ined, this was what kind of bu­reau. 霍雨浩的脸色很难看,以他的精神力,竟然飞了足有近半个时辰才发现不对,可想而知,这是一个怎样的局。 „What have you dis­cov­ered?” Tang Wu­tong asked in a low voice. “你发现了什么？”唐舞桐低声问道。 The Huo Yuhao forced smile said: „Be­fore be­cause, any­thing had not dis­cov­ered that there­fore so is pas­sive. Let me dis­cover in­cor­rect, is tem­per­a­ture.” 霍雨浩苦笑道:“正是因为之前什么都没发现,所以才如此被动。让我发现不对的,是温度。” „At our fly­ing speeds, if has flown in the Con­ti­nent di­rec­tion, then, flew to be so long, the tem­per­a­ture should in­crease is right, but, you dis­cov­ered not to have, the tem­per­a­ture not only has not in­creased, in­stead also re­duced. Es­pe­cially after fly­ing a mo­ment ago that re­gion, the scope that the tem­per­a­ture re­duces is quite not small.” “以我们的飞行速度,如果是一直朝着大陆方向飞行的话,那么,飞了这么久,温度应该有所增加才对,可是,你发现没有,温度不但没有增加,反而还降低了。尤其是在飞过刚才那片区域之后,温度降低的幅度还相当