s the ray puts greatly. 到了他们现在这种层次的修为,短时间内不呼吸还是不会有太大问题的。在搂紧唐舞桐的同时,霍雨浩额头上的命运之眼已经是光芒大放。 The golden-rose color halo il­lu­mi­nates the sur­round­ing sea water. Huo Yuhao then sees, be­yond being away from their sev­eral hun­dred me­ters, gath­ers round all kinds of sea Soul Beast at least sev­eral hun­dred. 玫瑰金色的光晕将周围的海水照亮。霍雨浩这才看到,就在距离他们数百米外,围着各种各样的海魂兽至少数百只之多。 And, in these sea Soul Beast, floats in the fore­front, im­pres­sively is an only beau­ti­ful mer­peo­ple, has the male to have the fe­male, in their hands grasps the lance or is being not the well-known coral, was gaz­ing at Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong, in the look has been full of the color of de­test­ing. 其中,这些海魂兽之中,漂浮在最前面的,赫然是一只只美丽的人鱼,有男有女,它们手中握着长矛或者是不知名的珊瑚,注视着霍雨浩和唐舞桐,眼神中都充满了憎恶之色。 Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power spreads by far, not only to­ward sur­round­ings, to­ward high and low. Comes am­pli­fi­ca­tion own Spir­i­tual De­tec­tion through Eye of Des­tiny, can in­ves­ti­gate the far­thest dis­tance. 霍雨浩的精神力远远扩散开来,不只是朝着周围,更是朝着上下。通过命运之眼来增幅自己的精神探测,才能探查到最远的距离。 He must find to out­side di­rec­tion first, then can seek for the break­through the op­por­tu­nity, oth­er­wise, can only by in dire straits here. Takes their cul­ti­vat­ing as, in adopts the breath to re­place the breath, longest also can only in­sist about half dou­ble-hour, more­over must con­sume Soul Power mas­sively. In other words, in half dou­ble-hour, them must be drown to death here. 他必须要先找到通往外面的方向,然后才能寻找突破的机会,否则的话,只能被困死在这里。以他们的修为,通过内息来代替呼吸,最长也只能坚持半个时辰左右,而且还要大量的消耗魂力。也就是说,半个时辰内冲不出去,他们就要被淹死在这里了。 „Hu­man­ity, do not make fu­tile ef­fort the mat­ter. Here is world of sea, the strength of sea will not make your Spir­i­tual Power be po­ten­tial achieve­ment. Your Spir­i­tual Power is strong, must be sup­pressed by the sea. This is the Sea God strength!” “人类,不要做徒劳的事情了。这里是大海的世界,海洋的力量是不会让你的精神力有所作为的。你的精神力再强,也要受到海洋的压制。这是海神的力量！” Is full of cold in­tent the mind thought to spread to the Huo Yuhao mind, Huo Yuhao sub­con­scious looks fol­low­ing this Spir­i­tual Po