the huge help func­tion to fu­ture sea Soul Beast, to that time, had many Soul Mas­ter not to need to hunt and kill Soul Beast to ob­tain Soul Ring. This is ab­solutely the best re­sult. 如果海魂兽一直将人类当做敌人,那么,未来的结果,只可能是腥风血雨。虽然冰海在日月帝国范围之内,但这也同样是霍雨浩不希望看到的。他希望自己的魂灵体系能够发扬光大,所以,这一次就变得非常重要。一旦他成功了,海公主就会信任他,对未来海魂兽也进入魂灵体系有着巨大的帮助作用,到了那时候,就有更多的魂师不需要猎杀魂兽就可以获得魂环了。这是绝对最好的结果。 There­fore, Huo Yuhao is will­ing to take risk to try. He can feel progress of own Spir­i­tual Power, as for whether to suc­ceed, he has not grasped, but must at­tempt, even if re­ceives heavy wound also to refuse to balk! 所以,霍雨浩才愿意冒险一试。他能感觉得到自己精神力的进步,至于能否成功,他没有把握,但总要去尝试,哪怕是自己受到重创也在所不惜！ At this mo­ment, the low and deep sound re­sounds, Sea Princess is bring­ing the [say / way] of sev­eral points of sob­bing: „Good, I agreed. Please get rid. Re­gard­less of the re­sult how, you are my sea clan for­ever friends.” 就在这时,低沉的声音响起,海公主带着几分哽咽的道:“好,我同意。请您出手吧。无论结果如何,你们都将是我海族永远的朋友。” Huo Yuhao looks to Sea Princess, has a look at her Mer­maid Princess again, then to has se­lected under one that they made an ef­fort, ar­rived by the Cold Jade bed. 霍雨浩看向海公主,再看看她身边的人鱼公主,然后向她们用力的点了一下头,重新来到寒玉床旁边。 If no ninth Soul Ring that Tang Wu­tong re­leases, they are how re­gard­less of not to be­lieve a hu­man­ity. How­ever, has light shadow that ninth Soul Ring has re­leased, the hos­til­i­ties in their heart com­pletely van­ished. More­over, while the hos­til­ity van­ishes, in this sea area, the vi­cious ten­den­cies in al­most all sea Soul Beast hearts were melted by that light shadow. 如果没有唐舞桐释放出的第九魂环,她们是无论如何也不会相信一个人类的。但是,有了那第九魂环释放出的光影,她们心中的敌意已经完全消失了。不仅如此,在敌意消失的同时,这片海域中,几乎所有海魂兽心中的戾气都被那个光影所化解。 At this mo­ment, in Sea Princess mother and daugh­ter heart, only then hopes. 此时此刻,海公主母女心中,就只有希冀。 Light ray twin­kle, on the Huo Yuhao face re­veals a ice-cold god light, the low and deep in­can­ta­tion re­cited the sound to start to re­sound. 淡淡的光芒闪烁,霍雨浩脸上流露出一丝冰冷神光,低沉的咒语吟唱声开始响起。 Here is the seabed, re­ceives the con­di­tion to limit, he did not have the means to por­tray demon for­ma­tion to as­sist, but that Mer­maid Princess con­di­tion also lets him to delay again, can only start im­me­di­ately. 这里是海底,受到条件所限,他已经没办法去刻画出魔法阵进行辅助了,而那位人鱼公主的状态也让他不能再拖延下去,只能立刻开始。

