DD2 - V.#11 - #545 The blessing of manatee


This time, it can be said that car­ried on the spirit fu­sion be­sides ini­tially and Snow Em­peror, a spirit that Huo Yuhao most has not grasped fused. But is also one of the he most im­por­tant spirit fu­sions. 这一次,可以说是除了当初和雪帝进行魂灵融合之外,霍雨浩最没把握的一次魂灵融合了。但也是他最重要的魂灵融合之一。 Low and deep in­can­ta­tion sound re­ver­ber­ates in the sea water, on Huo Yuhao, starts to send out the gen­tle mind fluc­tu­a­tion. This mind fluc­tu­ates, to the Sea Princess spread on Cold Jade bed in the past, re­leased the gen­tle aura. 低沉的咒语声在海水中回荡,霍雨浩身上,开始散发出柔和的精神波动。这精神波动,向寒玉床上的海公主蔓延过去,释放出轻柔的气息。 Sea Princess rests sinks and sinks very much very much. Her soul to shat­ter, in spir­i­tual sea Spir­i­tual Power drained close dry, own Soul Power was al­ready noth­ing left, the vi­tal­ity is not much left. This all, in­di­cates that she comes to the verge of death the con­di­tion now. 海公主睡的很沉、很沉。她的灵魂破碎,精神之海中精神力已经流失的接近干涸,自身魂力早已荡然无存,生命力所剩无几。这所有的一切,都预示着她现在濒临死亡的状态。 But, in such con­di­tion, she ac­tu­ally as be­fore is that beau­ti­ful, on her giant fish tail, is glit­ter­ing as be­fore the light golden gloss. 可是,就是在这样的状态下,她却依旧是那么美,她那巨大的鱼尾上,依旧闪烁着淡淡的金色光泽。 Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power is the pale golden color, in the recita­tion sound of in­can­ta­tion, cov­ers above her body, ex­ag­ger­ated her body to be many golden color, as if many vi­tal­ity. 霍雨浩的精神力是淡金色的,在咒语的吟唱声中,覆盖在她身体之上,渲染着她的身体都多了一层金色,也仿佛多了一层生命力似的。 Gen­tle in­can­ta­tion sound re­ver­ber­ates un­ceas­ingly, Huo Yuhao own body also sim­i­larly turned into the golden color, il­lu­sory magic six glow star light shadow ap­pear in his, the in­can­ta­tion started com­pletely. 柔和的咒语声不断回荡,霍雨浩自己的身体也同样变成了金色,虚幻的魔法六芒星光影出现在他脚下,咒语已经完全开始了。 Tang Wu­tong and Sea Princess mother and daugh­ter, closely are gaz­ing in side, in this seabed world, any out­side dan­ger may not say, the true dan­ger, came from in the process of fu­sion. 唐舞桐、海公主母女,都在旁边密切的注视着,在这海底世界,并没有任何外界危险可言,真正的危险,就源自于融合的过程。 No­body knew this fu­sion by what kind of sit­u­a­tion con­clu­sion, but in their hearts ac­tu­ally to suc­ceed to pray. 没人知道这份融合将会以怎样的情况结束,但她们心中却都在为了成功而祈祷。 , On Mer­maid Princess in that deep sleep started to have the strange aura to ap­pear grad­u­ally. That is such as the silk such as the wisp of pale golden halo. These halos out­ward re­lease from her fore­head, the golden halo con­geals above the fore­head qui­etly, the rich soul fluc­tu­a­tion also ap­pears. 渐渐的,那位沉睡中的人鱼公主身上开始有奇异的气息出现了。那是如丝如缕的淡金色光晕。这些光晕都是从她的头部向外释放而出的,金色光晕在头部上方悄然凝结,浓郁的灵魂波动也随之出现。 Sea Princess has got­ten hold of one­self daugh­ter's hand sub­con­sciously, she is very clear, the strength of that golden halo youngest daugh­ter's resid­ual soul. Once the strength of these souls are also de­feated and dis­persed, that. Youngest daugh­ter's life mark also for­ever van­ished from this world, true death. 海公主下意识的握紧了自己大女儿的手,她很清楚,那金色光晕正是小女儿残留的灵魂之力。而一旦这些灵魂之力也溃散的话,那么。小女儿的生命印记也就将永远的从这个世界消失了,真正的死亡。 On the Huo Yuhao face the look is as be­fore tran­quil, both hands are swing­ing in the air gen­tly, is co­or­di­nat­ing his in­can­ta­tion. 霍雨浩脸上神色依旧平静,双手在空气中轻轻的摆动着,配合着他的咒语。 Spirit Soul Power that Mer­maid Princess re­leases con­denses under the con­trol of Huo Yuhao grad­u­ally to­gether. Slowly changes into a face ap­pear­ance. Her ap­pear­ance. 那位人鱼公主释放出的灵魂力在霍雨浩的控制下渐渐凝聚在一起。缓缓的化为一张人脸模样。正是她自己的样貌。 Just, this face ap­pear­ance the strength of soul at this time not any ex­pres­sion. It seems is dif­fer­ent from deep sleep in she. 只不过,这人脸模样的灵魂之力此时没有任何表情。看上去就和沉睡中的她没什么两样。 This con­di­tion, mak­ing the Sea Princess mood very in­tense. She knows that Huo Yuhao this type re­duces the method of strength of daugh­ter soul only to con­tinue through Spir­i­tual Power some time, once he lets loose. Then, daugh­ter's the strength of soul is im­pos­si­ble to re­turn to the main body again. In other words, now does not have in­clud­ing op­por­tu­nity of re­gret. 这种状态,令海公主心情无比紧张。她知道,霍雨浩这种通过精神力来压缩女儿灵魂之力的方法只能持续一段时间而已,而一旦他放开。那么,女儿的灵魂之力是不可能再回到本体之中的了。也就是说,现在连后悔的机会都没有了。 Huo Yuhao will cer­tainly not re­gret that op