an­not achieve! At this mo­ment, under the stim­u­la­tion of Spir­i­tual Power, Mer­maid Princess in this deep sleep can see, only then a Huo Yuhao per­son, other sur­round­ings per­son of she is could not no­tice that she com­pletely im­merses in the in­can­ta­tion, has Huo Yuhao Spir­i­tual Power to ex­ag­ger­ate her, is con­sol­ing her. 一时间,海公主母女已经无比紧张,她是多么想要去劝慰自己的女儿啊！可是,她做不到,她根本做不到啊！此时此刻,在精神力的刺激下,这位沉睡中的人鱼公主能够看到的,就只有霍雨浩一个人,周围其他人她是看不到的,她完全是沉浸在咒语之中,只有霍雨浩的精神力在渲染着她,在劝慰着她。 „Not, not!” Strug­gling that Mer­maid Princess goes all out, en­tire con­tract in fierce is shiv­er­ing. The six glow stars of Huo Yuhao under foot even started to pre­sent the fis­sure. “不、不、不！”人鱼公主拼命的挣扎,整个契约都在剧烈的颤抖着。霍雨浩脚下的六芒星甚至开始出现了裂痕。 This Mer­maid Princess Spir­i­tual Power is ex­tremely for­mi­da­ble, even has striven to excel her elder sis­ter, even if the soul only re­main­ing parts, at this time, her full re­volt as be­fore made Huo Yuhao some­what un­able to sup­port. After all, when car­ries on the in­can­ta­tion, his one­self is com­pletely open, does not have any re­volt abil­ity. Com­plete, what­ever the soul of op­po­site party at­tacks. 这位人鱼公主的精神力极其强大,甚至要强过她的姐姐,哪怕灵魂只剩下一部分,在这个时候,她的全力反抗依旧令霍雨浩有些支撑不住了。毕竟,在进行咒语的时候,他自身是完全开放的,是没有任何反抗能力的。完全的任由对方的灵魂进行冲击。 The blood, flows fol­low­ing the Huo Yuhao mouth, nose and ear slowly under. At this time, com­pletely was the con­test of Spir­i­tual Power, no, can­not say is the con­test, should per­suade. If Huo Yuhao can­not suc­ceed con­vinced this Mer­maid Princess, then, he def­i­nitely by in­tensely back­lash, more­over can, the fail­ure! 鲜血,顺着霍雨浩口、鼻、耳缓缓流淌而下。在这个时候,完全是精神力的较量,不,不能说是较量,应该是劝服。如果霍雨浩不能成功的说服这位人鱼公主,那么,他必然会受到强烈的反噬,而且会,失败！ The Tang Wu­tong dou­ble fist grips tightly, at this time, no one could help Huo Yuhao. This com­pletely is the ex­change on mind, and has noth­ing to do with the Spir­i­tual Power strong and weak. 唐舞桐双拳紧握,在这个时候,谁也帮不了霍雨浩。这完全是精神上的交流,而且与精神力强弱无关。 This type of equal con­tract, in the sit­u­a­tion that need­ing both sides com­ple