海在她那强悍的精神力撞击下已经开始出现了细微的裂痕。 It is not good, per­haps, or was good. In Huo Yuhao heart se­cret forced smile, he can­not use his life to re­ceive in ex­change for more time! Also has ex­is­tences of an­other five big spir­its in his spir­i­tual sea, once spir­i­tual sea re­ceives heavy wound, these five big spir­its will also be dam­aged. 不行了,恐怕真的要不行了。霍雨浩心中暗暗苦笑,他不能用自己的生命来换取更多的时间啊！在他精神之海中还有另外五大魂灵的存在,一旦精神之海受到重创,这五大魂灵也会受创。 In the heart sighed one darkly, al­though Huo Yuhao ex­tremely did not hope, but he also un­der­stood at this time, one­self sim­ply did not have other means that can only be the choice gives up. 心中暗叹一声,霍雨浩虽然万分不愿,但他也明白在这个时候,自己根本没有其他办法,只能是选择放弃。 The con­tract car­ries on here, has achieved ** con­di­tion, the soul of both sides started to con­tact, even if that Mer­maid Princess in ex­treme repel Huo Yuhao, both sides soul under equal con­tract func­tion, there is an op­por­tu­nity of con­tact. 契约进行到这里,已经达到了最**状态,双方的灵魂已经开始接触了,哪怕是那人鱼公主在极度的排斥霍雨浩,双方灵魂在平等契约地作用下,也有接触的机会。 This has at­tempted fi­nally, after the con­tact, if this Mer­maid Princess was un­able some­what to change for the bet­ter, Huo Yuhao must ter­mi­na­tion coura­geously, oth­er­wise, he will pos­si­bly re­ceive ir­re­triev­able heavy wound. 这是最后的尝试了,接触之后,如果这位人鱼公主还不能有几分好转的话,霍雨浩就必须当机立断的终止,否则,他很可能会受到不可挽回的重创。 The soul of both sides moved gen­tly, just like Huo Yuhao was ex­pected that such, the Mer­maid Princess soul looks like the fright­ened fawn com­mon in­stan­ta­neous ball opens sim­ply. 双方的灵魂轻轻的碰触了一下,正如霍雨浩预料中的那样,人鱼公主的灵魂简直就像是受惊的小鹿一般瞬间弹开。 It is not good, is not good, can give up re­ally? 不行,还是不行,真的要放弃了吗？ Flood bit­ter and as­trin­gent time in the Huo Yuhao heart, the hys­te­ria mood of sud­denly, in the Mer­maid Princess soul send­ing out has stopped, she was sim­i­lar some delay, that face stag­nated in air­borne, looks at Huo Yuhao. 正在霍雨浩心中泛起苦涩的时候,突然,人鱼公主灵魂中散发出的歇斯底里情绪停顿了一下,紧接着,她仿佛有些呆滞了似的,那张面庞停滞在空中,怔怔的看着霍雨浩。 Um? Did she no longer at­tack me? No longer does the at­tempt get rid? 嗯？她不再攻击我了？不再尝试摆脱？ Huo Yuhao some­what is also be­wil­dered, he had tried hard not to have the half minute re­sult a mo­ment ago, why at this mo­ment, he must give up, mean­ing that this Mer­maid Princess as if has ac­tu­ally ro­tated? 霍雨浩也有些莫名其妙,刚才他已经那么努力了都没有半分结果,为什么这一刻,他已经要放弃了,这位人鱼公主却仿佛有所回转的意思？ In this time, in the Huo Yuhao soul, a light Bai Se (White Color) ray is not hav­ing the emer­gence of omen, that Bai Se (White Color) ray was not con­trolled by Huo Yuhao, un­ex­pect­edly has sep­a­rated, float in midair. 正在这时,霍雨浩的灵魂之中,一层淡淡的白色光芒毫无预兆的出现了,那一点白色光芒并不受到霍雨浩的控制,居然就那么分离了出来,悬浮于半空之中。 This Bai Se (White Color) ray spreads qui­etly, in­creases, changed an image un­ex­pect­edly. Im­pres­sively this Mer­maid Princess ap­pear­ance! 紧接着,这白色光芒悄然扩散,变大,竟然变化成了一幅图像。赫然正是这位人鱼公主的模样啊！ Saw this, Huo Yuhao has shocked, the Sea Princess mother and daugh­ter sim­i­larly were also shocked. 看到这一幕,霍雨浩震惊了,海公主母女也同样震惊了。 This is...... 这是…… This clearly is Soul Source! Al­though has one, but in this Soul Source seems ac­tu­ally mix­ing with any thing. 这分明是灵魂本源啊！虽然只有一丝,但这一丝灵魂本源之中却仿佛夹杂着什么东西似的。 The white light dodges, fell on that Mer­maid Princess, im­me­di­ately, the mood of her hys­te­ria one com­pletely was tran­quil, looks that the Huo Yuhao very panic-stricken vi­sion also in­stan­ta­neously had the trans­for­ma­tion. 白光一闪,就落在了那位人鱼公主身上,顿时,她歇斯底里的情绪一下就完全平静了下来,看着霍雨浩原本十分惊恐的目光也瞬间就发生了转变。 Her vi­sion be­came gen­tle, looks at Huo Yuhao, seemed sigh­ing gen­tly. Her soul also starts to change, had the face to exist, at this time in­creases un­ex­pect­edly grad­u­ally, changed the body, com­pletely was a small mer­maid ap­pear­ance float in the midair. 她的目光变得柔和了,看着霍雨浩,似乎在轻轻的叹息着。她的灵魂也开始发生变化,原本只是有面庞存在,此时竟是渐渐变大,变出了身体,完全是一条小小的美人鱼模样悬浮在半空之中。 This...... 这…… „This is......, The bless­ing of mer­peo­ple.” Sea Princess was ex­claim­ing in sur­prise said. “这是……,人鱼的祝福。”海公主惊叹着说道。 Tang Wu­tong puz­zled looks to Sea Princess, said: „Se­nior, what is the bless­ing of mer­peo­ple?” 唐舞桐不解的看向海公主,道:“前辈,人鱼的祝福是什么？” -------------------