Sea Princess said: „A our mer­peo­ple clan grows per­cep­ti­bly by Spir­i­tual Power, each has the op­por­tu­nity that one time blessed in the life. Per­son who blessed, will ob­tain luck­ily, more­over is our mer­peo­ple clan for­ever friend. If a clan peo­ple, this is the per­for­mance of pro­fess­ing love. On this hu­man­ity, ac­tu­ally has the bless­ing of mer­peo­ple . More­over, mer­peo­ple bless­ing that more­over my piti­ful daugh­ter re­leases prob­a­bly! This and are this pos­si­ble? Ac­tu­ally to have had what?” 海公主道:“我们人鱼一族以精神力见长,每一位在一生之中都拥有一次祝福的机会。被祝福的人,将获得幸运,而且将是我们人鱼一族永远的朋友。如果是本族中人,这更是示爱的表现。这位人类身上,竟然有着人鱼的祝福,而且、而且好像正是我那可怜女儿释放出的人鱼祝福啊！这、这怎么可能？究竟发生过什么？” Tang Wu­tong re­mem­bers the sit­u­a­tion that has fought im­me­di­ately, sur­prised [say / way]: „I knew prob­a­bly what's the mat­ter. At that time we col­lab­o­rated, strike to kill that to per­se­cute your daugh­ter's Evil Soul Mas­ter, in that Evil Soul Mas­ter Wraith Soul, had ex­is­tence of mer­peo­ple ap­pear­ance. Yuhao pu­ri­fies her with own Power of Pu­rifi­ca­tion, then that mer­peo­ple Wraith Soul be­fore the dis­si­pa­tion, re­leased a white light to fall on Yuhao, likely was the mer­peo­ple that you said blesses?” 唐舞桐顿时想起了那一战的情况,惊讶的道:“我好像知道是怎么回事了。当时我们联手,击杀了那名迫害您女儿的邪魂师,在那邪魂师的怨灵中,就有一位人鱼模样的存在。雨浩用自己的净化之力将她净化,然后那人鱼怨灵在消散之前,就释放出了一点白光落在了雨浩身上,很可能就是您所说的人鱼祝福了吧？” Sea Princess bursts into tears in­stan­ta­neously once more, this time, ac­tu­ally no longer is the golden tears, but is the pure white pearl. This is the happy tears, is the ashamed tears, be­fore one­self is ashamed in view of Huo Yuhao and Tang Wu­tong be­hav­ior, can have the op­por­tu­nity to live to be happy for the daugh­ter. 海公主瞬间再次流泪,这一次,却不再是金色的眼泪,而是洁白的珍珠。这是幸福的泪水啊,同时也是惭愧的泪水,为自己之前针对霍雨浩和唐舞桐的行为而惭愧,为了女儿能够有机会活下来而幸福。 Yes, after ob­tain­ing the fu­sion of mer­peo­ple bless­ing, that Mer­maid Princess as if has rec­og­nized Huo Yuhao, in the look did not have again panic-stricken, is kind and grate­ful. 是的,得到了人鱼祝福的融合之后,那位人鱼公主仿佛已经认出了霍雨浩,眼神之中再没有