. 人鱼公主并没有吸收这些金光,当霍雨浩的咒语最终完成时,她的娇躯已经完全变成了金色,鱼尾轻轻一摆,她就落在了霍雨浩的肩头上。 Orig­i­nally re­gard­ing in Huo Yuhao air bub­ble in­stan­ta­neous to shat­ter, but, Huo Yuhao does not have the feel­ing that the least bit suf­fo­cates. As if the air from emerges in his pore in all di­rec­tions. More­over, ob­vi­ous that very he feels, own Spir­i­tual Power is pro­mot­ing at an ex­cep­tional pace, more­over as if has not got­ten on­line. Spir­i­tual Sys­tem Soul Nu­cleus is ex­pand­ing. Is turned into the bright golden color by the pale golden color that the [gold/metal] pearl ex­ag­ger­ated un­ex­pect­edly. His en­tire spir­i­tual sea al­most ex­panded more than one-third . More­over, in spir­i­tual sea, sea water al­ready, not only vis­cous, even turned into the solid state. More­over the lus­ter was also pro­founder. 原本围绕在霍雨浩身边的气泡瞬间破碎,但是,霍雨浩却没有半点窒息的感觉。仿佛空气是从四面八方涌入他的毛孔之中似的。而且,他感觉的很明显,自己的精神力正在以惊人的速度提升着,而且似乎没有上线似的。精神系魂核在扩大。原本被金珍珠渲染出的淡金色竟是变成了灿金色。他整个精神之海几乎扩大了1多,而且,精神之海内,海水已经不只是粘稠,甚至是变成了固态。而且色泽也更加深邃了。 For­mi­da­ble Spir­i­tual Power al­most along with the thought out­ward dif­fu­sion, shows the sea level di­rectly, all in sur­round­ings sea, en­tire seabed palace, com­pletely in his sen­sa­tion. 强大的精神力几乎随着意念向外扩散,直接透出海面,周围大海中的一切,整个海底宫殿,也完全都在他的感知之中。 Mer­maid Princess saw own mother and elder sis­ter fi­nally, in her eye pupil, is re­veal­ing the sad color, but also sim­i­larly has one type the joy of ob­tain­ing fresh­man. This time she, is un­sta­ble as the spirit. There­fore, she was un­able to speak. 人鱼公主终于看到了自己的母亲和姐姐,在她的眼眸之中,流露着悲伤之色,但也同样有一种获得新生的欣喜。此时的她,作为魂灵还并不稳定。所以,她还不能说话。 A fish tail gen­tly pen­du­lum, air­borne from her body the golden halo drifted about im­me­di­ately, falls on own elder sis­ter. 鱼尾轻轻一摆,空中从她身体所化的金色光晕顿时漂荡了出去,落在自己姐姐身上。 Im­me­di­ately, the royal crown on that sil­ver crown Mer­maid Princess top of the head turned into the golden color, the sil­ver fish tail also sim­i­larly turned into the golden color. 顿时,那位银冠人鱼公主头顶上的冠冕变成了金色,银色的鱼尾也同样变成了金色。 This is the strength of blood­lines! Be­com­ing the Mer­maid Princess of Huo Yuhao spirit, fuses own blood­lines strength, has trans­mit­ted one­self elder sis­ter's body com­pletely. 这是血脉的力量！成为霍雨浩魂灵的这位人鱼公主,将自己的血脉力量融合起来,已经完全传递到了自己姐姐的身上。 This also in­her­ited the golden blood­lines of Mer­maid Princess, her elder sis­ter will con­tinue this blood­lines in­her­i­tance, be­comes next Sea Princess. Also is she keeps in seabed sea clan the final thing. From now hence­forth, she no longer is the princess in icy seas, but is the Huo Yuhao sixth spirit! 这也是将人鱼公主的黄金血脉传承了下去,她的姐姐就会将这份血脉传承继续下去,成为下一位的海公主。也是她留在海底海族之中最后的东西。从今以后,她不再是冰海中的公主,而是霍雨浩的第六魂灵！ The Sea Princess mother and daugh­ter have had tears stream­ing down the face. 海公主母女已是泪流满面。 Huo Yuhao knows through the mem­ory of one­self mer­peo­ple spirit that with the lit­tle princess who he fuses, the name is Li Ya, but her elder sis­ter, the name is Li Jing. 霍雨浩通过自己人鱼魂灵的记忆知道,与他融合的这位小公主,名字叫做丽雅,而她的姐姐,名字叫做丽晶。 Light ray twin­kle, on the Huo Yuhao face re­veals a smile, „se­nior, the good for­tune does not fail in one's mis­sion. Al­though the princess can­not ressurec­tion, but at least lived by an­other con­di­tion. So long as I am also liv­ing, she has ex­isted.” 淡淡的光芒闪烁,霍雨浩脸上流露出一丝微笑,“前辈,幸不辱命。虽然公主殿下没能复活,但至少以另一种状态活了下来。只要我还活着,她就会一直存在着。” Spoke these words, Huo Yuhao is sit­ting cross-legged to sit down im­me­di­ately same place, en­tered the med­i­tate con­di­tion. Al­though this Mer­maid Princess be­fore be­com­ing spirit ap­proached the oil com­pletely lamp dry con­di­tion, but she must un­ex­pect­edly be in­her­i­tance of mer­peo­ple lin­eage/vein gold blood­lines! Own mind level is greatly strength­ened, by strength, above elder sis­ter Li Jing. 说完这句话,霍雨浩立刻在原地盘膝坐下,进入了冥想状态。这位人鱼公主虽然在成为魂灵之前已经接近了油尽灯枯的状态,但她必竟是人鱼一脉黄金血脉的传承者啊！自身的精神层次极强,论实力,更在姐姐丽晶之上。 Huo Yuhao fused her spirit, own spir­i­tual sea rises sud­denly, Soul Nu­cleus pre­sented the evo­lu­tion, he re­quires the time to di­gest and ad­just­ment. 霍雨浩融合了她的魂灵,自身精神之海暴涨,就连魂核都出现了进化,他需要时间来消化和调整。 The white light dodges, Snow Em­peror emerges out of thin air in front of Sea Princess, vis­its her with smile on the face, said: „Sea Princess, you do not think now I am fake?” 白光一闪,雪帝凭空出现在海公主面前,面带微笑的看着她,道:“海公主,现在你不会认为我是假的了吧？” Sea Princess some­what ashamed low­er­ing the head, said: „Sorry, Snow Em­peror, I was hated have be­come con­fused. If not for Sir Sea God re­minded, per­haps we re­ally cast the blun­der. Snow Em­peror my some are not clear, you and Ice Em­peror, why be­came his spirit, on this, there is what spe­cial place?” 海公主有些羞惭的低下头,道:“抱歉,雪帝,我被仇恨冲昏了头脑。若不是海神大人提醒,恐怕我们就真的铸成大错了。只是,雪帝我有些不明白,你和冰帝,为什么都成为了他的魂灵,难道在这位身上,有什么特异的地方吗？” Snow Em­peror sighed spook­ily, said: „Said that he has the per­son of big chance, you come out.” 雪帝幽幽一叹,道:“说起来,他是有大机缘的人,你们都出来吧。” With a Snow Em­peror sum­mon, an­other four big spir­its also all from the Huo Yuhao within the body sep­a­ra­tion, ap­pear in front of Sea Princess. 伴随着雪帝一声呼唤,另外四大魂灵也全都从霍雨浩体内分离而出,出现在海公主面前。 Snow Em­peror said: „I give you to in­tro­duce first. Bing'er you are the un­der­stand­ing, I was not many say. This is Day­dream. On cul­ti­vat­ing is, ac­tu­ally it was ini­tially most pow­er­house on our Ex­treme North Tun­dra, is now on Con­ti­nent, only sur­passed for 1 mil­lion years to cul­ti­vate for ex­isted.” 雪帝道:“我先给你介绍一下。冰儿你是认识的,我就不多说了。这位是天梦。论修为,其实它才是当初我们极北冰原上的最强者,也是当今大陆上,唯一一位超过了1000000年修为的存在。” Sea Princess sur­prised looks at Day­dream Ice Silk­worm, „1 mil­lion years......” this type cul­ti­vated over 600,000 years of pow­er­house to be very clear to the later pe­riod wanted to carry on the break­through to be dif­fi­cult, Ex­treme North Tun­dra re­ally had Soul Beast to prac­tice to 1 mil­lion years of bound­ary, this sim­ply was too in­con­ceiv­able. 海公主惊讶的看着天梦冰蚕,“1000000年……”她这种修炼了超过600000年的强者很清楚到了后期想要进行突破有多么困难,极北冰原竟然有魂兽能够修炼到1000000年境界,这简直是太不可思议了。 The Day­dream Ice Silk­worm forced smile said: „Snow Em­peror, do not dirty me, my this is any 1 mil­lion years, but was being kept think­ing about by in­nu­mer­able Soul Beast food. Sea Princess, I know that you did not feel re­lieved your youngest daugh­ter fol­lowed Yuhao, ac­tu­ally, you lis­ten to me to nar­rate that his ex­pe­ri­ence also un­der­stood.” 天梦冰蚕苦笑道:“雪帝,你就别埋汰我了,我这算什么1000000年,不过是被无数魂兽惦记着的食物罢了。海公主,我知道你不放心自己的小女儿跟了雨浩,其实,你听听我讲述他的经历也就明白了。” At that mo­ment, since Day­dream Ice Silk­worm at first and Huo Yuhao meets from one­self says, nar­rated how he be­comes Huo Yuhao first Soul Ring, how af­ter­ward to make Ice Em­peror Huo Yuhao sec­ond Mar­tial Soul. 当下,天梦冰蚕从自己最初和霍雨浩相遇之时讲起,讲述了他是如何成为霍雨浩第一魂环,后来又是如何让冰帝成为霍雨浩第二武魂。 Such that just like Snow Em­peror said that the fu­sion of Ice Em­peror, Snow Em­peror and Day­dream Ice Silk­worm and Huo Yuhao can de­scribe with the chance co­in­ci­dence. But Oc­tag­o­nal Mys­te­ri­ous Ice Grass and Xiao Bai (Lit­tle White), were ac­tu­ally their own choices. 正如雪帝所说的那样,冰帝、雪帝和天梦冰蚕与霍雨浩的融合都可以用机缘巧合来形容。而八角玄冰草和小白,却是它们自身的选择了。 After lis­ten­ing to nar­ra­tion of Day­dream Ice Silk­worm, Sea Princess un­der­stood fi­nally why on this hu­man­ity will have the so mys­te­ri­ous place. Ac­tu­ally can achieve­ment spirit type never pre­sent spe­cial ex­is­tence. 听了天梦冰蚕的讲述之后,海公主总算是明白了为什么这个人类身上会有如此神奇的地方。竟然能够成就魂灵这种从未出现过的特殊存在。 Snow Em­peror said: „We fol­low Yuhao at first, ac­tu­ally does not have any con­fi­dence. But with the lapse of time, his moral char­ac­ter and abil­ity, ob­tained our ap­proval. When Day­dream at first with he fuses the ten­ta­tive plan, he is mak­ing great strides for­ward sta­bly. If one day, he re­ally can take that step, then, we also to­gether as­cended to heaven with him, are sep­a­rated from the limit of this world.” 雪帝道:“最初我们跟随雨浩,其实都是没有任何信心的。但随着时间的推移,他的品性、能力,都得到了我们的认可。天梦最初与他融合时的设想,他正在稳定的迈进着。如果有一天,他真的能够迈出那一步,那么,我们也就都跟着他一起升天,脱离这个世界的限制了。” Lis­tened to a Snow Em­peror such say­ing, the dou­ble pupil of Sea Princess also to shine, Snow Em­peror and Ice Em­peror they no doubt in gam­bling, but has con­cen­trated the so for­mi­da­ble strength, the des­tiny of this hu­man­ity has been the ex­tremely high de­gree, per­haps, he had the op­por­tu­nity to break the limit of this world, to that time...... 听雪帝这么一说,海公主的双眸也不禁亮了起来,雪帝和冰帝他们固然是在赌,但集中了如此强大的力量,这个人类的气运已经达到了极高的程度,说不定,他真的有机会能够突破这个世界的限制,到了那时候…… En­vies and gives free reign to the imag­i­na­tion al­most si­mul­ta­ne­ously ap­pears in the Sea Princess heart, after long time, she sup­presses im­pul­sive that one­self in­ner­most feel­ings had. 羡慕与畅想几乎同时出现在海公主心中,半晌之后,她才压制住了自己内心出现的一丝冲动。 Sea Princess is very clear, her daugh­ter be­came the Huo Yuhao spirit, that has a hope of this mer­peo­ple clan. Al­though she also some such hopes, but she cul­ti­vated to just break through shortly after for 600,000 years, but also there are pos­si­ble to live for a long time, sea Soul Beast in icy seas also needed her, said again that wanted to turn into a god, that even­tu­ally was the il­lu­sory mat­ter! There­fore, she re­pressed the im­pul­sion of one­self in­ner­most feel­ings even­tu­ally. 海公主很清楚,自己的女儿已经成为霍雨浩的魂灵了,那就是带这人鱼一族的希望。她虽然也有这样的渴望,但她修为刚刚突破600000年不久,还有很长时间可活,冰海中的海魂兽们也需要她,再说,想要成神,那终究是虚无缥缈的事情啊！所以,她终究还是按捺住了自己内心的冲动。 The vi­sion changes nearby Tang Wu­tong, Sea Princess re­spect­ful ask­ing: „You and Sir Sea God are......” 目光转向一旁的唐舞桐,海公主恭敬的问道:“那您和海神大人是……” Not only Sea Princess and Mer­maid Princess Li Jing, the Huo Yuhao five big spirit same fash­ion have also re­vealed the cu­ri­ous color. 不只是海公主和人鱼公主丽晶,霍雨浩的五大魂灵也都同时流露出了好奇之色。 Today this war, af­ter­ward change can say that is be­cause Tang Wu­tong pro­duces. If no that [say / way] strange light shadow that Tang Wu­tong sum­moned, per­haps they will down­cast here, Huo Yuhao al­ready died at this time. 今天这一战,后来的变化可以说全都是因为唐舞桐才产生的。如果没有唐舞桐召唤出的那道奇异光影,恐怕他们都将陷落在这里,霍雨浩此时早已身亡。 Tang Wu­tong gives a calm smile, said: „My final Soul Abil­ity, name is, Sea God De­scend.” 唐舞桐淡然一笑,道:“我最后的魂技,名字叫做,海神降临。” Ninth Soul Abil­ity, Sea God De­scend! 第九魂技,海神降临！ The body of Sea Princess shiv­ered slightly, mut­tered the tun­nel: „Sea God De­scend, re­ally and is re­ally Sir Sea God!” She gains ground looks once more to Tang Wu­tong, sees, is the Tang Wu­tong eye in­clud­ing the pupil light of pro­found mean­ing, has not asked again, but re­spect­ful bows to Tang Wu­tong for the rit­ual. 海公主的身体略微颤抖了一下,喃喃地道:“海神降临,果然、果然是海神大人啊！”她抬头再次看向唐舞桐,看到的,是唐舞桐眼含深意的眸光,没有再问下去,只是恭敬的向唐舞桐躬身为礼。 Tang Wu­tong re­turns salute, does not have to ex­plain one again. 唐舞桐还礼,却没有再多解释一句。 Ice Em­peror and Snow Em­peror look at each other one, looks that Tang Wu­tong re­vealed the sur­prised color. 冰帝、雪帝对视一眼,看着唐舞桐都流露出了惊讶之色。 ---------------------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------- Sought the monthly ticket and rec­om­men­da­tion vote sup­port again, the Magic Chef of Ice and Fire car­toon five launched in salvos. Every­body ex­am­ines in our pres­tige plat­form. 再求月票、推荐票支持,冰火魔厨漫画五连发了哦。大家在我们威信平台上查看。

