„Likes the north­ern am­mo­nia being cold! In that side, my bat­tle ef­fi­ciency at least in­creases 30%.” Huo Yuhao is feel­ing some­what hot and damp air, but said. “还是更喜欢北方的氨冷啊！在那边,我的战斗力起码增加三成。”霍雨浩感受着有些湿热的空气,无奈说道。 The Tang Wu­tong cov­er­ing the mouth chuckle, said: „Hasn't the tour of icy seas, given your enough les­son?” 唐舞桐掩口轻笑,道:“冰海之行,还没给你足够的教训么？” Nod of Huo Yuhao deep to be so, said: „Nat­u­rally gave my enough les­son, the tour of this icy seas, told me, do not go into oth­ers den to fight oth­ers. Re­ally an op­por­tu­nity does not have. Al­though Sea Princess is for­mi­da­ble, but if on the land, or in a rel­a­tively fair point place, we can­not hit, runs greatly has the op­por­tu­nity. May in the icy seas deep place, that re­ally be as­cends the sky road­less, en­ters does not have the gate.” 霍雨浩深以为然的点了点头,道:“当然给我足够的教训了,这次冰海之行,实打实的告诉我,一定不要跑到人家老巢里跟人家动手。真是一点机会都没有。海公主虽然强大,可如果是在陆地上,或者是在一个相对公平点的地方,我们打不过,跑还是大有机会的。可在冰海深处,那就真的是上天无路、入地无门了。” Tang Wu­tong said: „Did goal elect?” 唐舞桐道:“目标选好了？” Huo Yuhao nod­ded, has re­ferred to the map. 霍雨浩点了点头,在地图上指了指。 Pleased Sea City! 海悦城！ The Huo Yuhao cor­ners of the mouth place out­lined to wipe the smile, this place he was not first time came, ini­tially, their Tang Sect peo­ple en­tered in Sun-Moon Em­pire from the wa­ter­way qui­etly, res­cued be­longs to the Douluo Con­ti­nent three coun­tries par­tic­i­pates in the Great Con­ti­nen­tal Soul Mas­ter Acad­emy Fight­ing Spirit Com­pe­ti­tion youth tal­ents, passed through this Pleased Sea City, more­over ships that also here rented. 霍雨浩嘴角处勾勒起一抹微笑,这地方他可不是第一次来了,当初,他们唐门众人从水路悄然进入日月帝国境内,营救原属斗罗大陆三国参加全大陆高级魂师学院斗魂大赛的青年才俊们,就是经过了这海悦城,而且也正是在这里租用的船只。 At­tack judg­ment this city, one is be­cause here is the Sun-Moon Em­pire south sea area strate­gic place, an­other also to con­fuse the Sun-Moon Em­pire as­pect, mak­ing them at least pro­duce and the oth­ers to be pos­si­ble be en­ters the thought of bor­der from the coastal ter­ri­tory. 选择攻击这座城市,一个是因为这里乃是日月帝国南方海域重镇,另一个也是为了迷惑日月帝国方面,让他们至少会产