into the Sun-Moon Em­pire do­main. 前线方面在五天前就传来了好消息,已占领天魂帝国除史莱克城之外的全境。这也意味着,天魂帝国真正的完全被毁灭了,并入日月帝国版图之中。 This good news Xu Tian­ran this re­straint strength greatly strength­ened to be stewed to the gills. 这个好消息让徐天然这种克制力极强的人都大醉了一场。 But, the good news to pass on a few days , the bad news pours. 可是,好消息才传回来没几天,坏消息就接踵而至。 Soul En­gi­neer Corp that in the north re­belled did not have the trail through­out, looked like has not ex­isted. But south ac­tu­ally suf­fered the in­tense at­tack, for sev­eral days, Xu Tian­ran re­ceived being in dan­ger of south­ern 12 cities. Area the south­ern coast, is a con­fu­sion. Every­body feels in­se­cure. 之前在北方作乱的魂导师团始终没有踪迹,就像是从来都没存在过似的。可南方却又遭受到了强烈的攻击,短短几天时间内,徐天然已经收到了南方12座城市的告急。南方沿海一带,已经是一片混乱。人人自危。 Must know, coast of the south, is the im­por­tant source of in­come of Sun-Moon Em­pire, the yearly in­come of that side medium city, is equal to the north­ern big city suf­fi­ciently. 要知道,南方沿海,乃是日月帝国的重要经济来源,那边一座中型城市的年收入,足以相当于北方一座大城市。 12 cities were looted, al­though the ca­su­alty fig­ure is not big, the south that but this cre­ates is scared as well as the de­struc­tion is enor­mous. The south is flus­tered, this will def­i­nitely vac­il­late his rule! 12座城市被洗劫,虽然伤亡数字都不大,但这造成的南方恐慌以及破坏却是极大的。南方人心惶惶,这必然会动摇他的统治啊！ Sev­eral days ago also in the north­ern that group of peo­ple, un­ex­pect­edly to the south? Is this pos­si­ble? 难道说,十几天前还在北方的那群人,竟然神不知鬼不觉的到了南方？这怎么可能？ „Your majesty! The feu­dal of­fi­cials think that these evil­do­ers the sea route of pos­si­ble is takes.” The prime min­is­ter sink­ing sound said. “陛下！臣以为,这些贼子很可能是走的海路。”首相沉声说道。 Xu Tian­ran looks to him, „sea route? North they at­tacked be­fore, how pos­si­bly to ar­rive from sea route?” 徐天然看向他,“海路？他们之前袭击北方,从海路怎么可能抵达？” The Sun-Moon Em­pire north is the icy seas, more­over icy seas ad­join to Ex­treme North Tun­dra. The Ex­treme North Tun­dra bad weather, no­body knows rad­i­cally a far­ther place is any ap­pear­ance. To by­pass Ex­treme North Tun­dra from the north, that is at all the im­pos